data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to your new home nestled in a tranquil neighborhood! This residence boasts an inviting open layout, seamlessly connecting the family room, kitchen, dining room, and living room. The kitchen is a chef's dream with abundant cabinet space, granite countertops, a convenient walk-in pantry, a kitchen island, and a breakfast bar for casual meals. The primary bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom. The ensuite is adorned with a dual sink vanity, complemented by granite countertops, and a rejuvenating standalone shower adorned with new tile. Venture upstairs to discover a generous game room, perfect for entertainment and relaxation. Two additional bedrooms await, each adorned with walk-in closets, ensuring ample storage space. The full-size bathroom on this level is equipped with a single sink vanity, granite countertops, and a shower/tub combo. Step outside into the fully fenced backyard. The covered patio provides a perfect setting for outdoor gatherings, offering both shade and comfort. The expansive green space is ideal for recreational activities or creating your own private garden oasis. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
